- Modernized "Playback Speed", "Sleep Timer", and "New Playlist" dialogs with an edge-to-edge design.
- The "Playback Speed" dialog now includes a precise slider (0.25x-8.0x), step buttons, and presets for quick adjustments.
- Refined various UI elements like buttons and corner radius's for a softer, more consistent look.
- Improved artwork fetching logic to prevent incorrect caching of missing embedded art.
- Enabled Gradle configuration cache to improve build performance.